title: Thales Payshield 10K Device State
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/Payshield
license: Proprietary
distribution: Proprietary
description:
 This check monitors the device state of a Thales Payshield HSM via SNMP. It reports whether the device is in Secure, Offline, or Online state based on the SNMP value:

 - 0 = Secure (WARN): Both keys on the HSM are turned ON, device is offline and in secure state (expected during Key Ceremony).
 - 1 = Offline (WARN): One key is turned ON, device is in offline mode (expected during maintenance).
 - 2 = Online (OK): Device is online and operational.

inventory:
 This check does not create inventory entries.


